name: Zombie black
description:
This shirt was designed and created by Angelo Parente of the band Motionless in White!!! Please show some love not only to us but to them as well.

All our shirts are printed on American Apparel tees and will fit tight. So make sure you know the proper size that fits your body :)

Be advised, we are going to wait until all our shirts have been ordered before we ship them out. Which means that the wait time for you to receive your shirt might be a week or two. Feel free to contact us for more information.

name: Memories
description:
This shirt was created because we want people to know that you should not forget your memories, whether they be good or bad. They never fade because they make us who we are and we should never forget anything in this journey that we call life.

All purchases made will go towards a special streamer I know called  TheThauglor on twitch tv

name: Clouded Judgement
description: This shirt was inspired by those of you who let others influence the decisions you make in life but still have hope to one day break free of the hold they have on you.
